    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted this package under the Minimal profile for internal tracking purposes. All 13 credibility factors have been enumerated with required and achieved levels. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The overall achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors, indicating significant credibility gaps that would need remediation before regulatory submission. Package is accepted as a record of the current state of evidence.",
